  "detailed_description": "Take control of a new prototype spaceship that's been shrunken by new military technology to defeat the Rogue AI which threatens billions of lives with a potential black hole event.<br><br>However, upon infiltration your spaceship has been partially hacked, preventing you from slowing down! Skilfully avoid obstacles controlled by the Rogue AI and ultimately destroy the \"Mega-Brain\".<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109600/extras/9c35817f552e0808b9d91bf52fa8fa4c.poster.avif?t=1696030081\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109600/extras/9c35817f552e0808b9d91bf52fa8fa4c.webm?t=1696030081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109600/extras/9c35817f552e0808b9d91bf52fa8fa4c.mp4?t=1696030081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Master the use of your Boost, Shield, Missiles and Guns to beat the Campaign and unlock Special Operations! Or test your skills in the Infinite Levels that range from Easy to Hard to achieve a High Score on each one.<br><br>All game modes will reward you with Ship Parts which are used to purchase new and better spaceships!<br><br>Fight against the Rogue AI Cyborgs who try to stop you!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109600/extras/e308a9a9cf1be38d7740bcc163050491.poster.avif?t=1696030081\" width=600 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109600/extras/e308a9a9cf1be38d7740bcc163050491.webm?t=1696030081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109600/extras/e308a9a9cf1be38d7740bcc163050491.mp4?t=1696030081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Use your Shield system to become temporarily immune to all damage, as one hit or crash would normally kill you.<br><br>Shoot your missile to deal heavy AoE damage, push certain objects or destroy asteroids and mines.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109600/extras/ced0c434621228443e7e69f560223ca1.poster.avif?t=1696030081\" width=600 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109600/extras/ced0c434621228443e7e69f560223ca1.webm?t=1696030081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109600/extras/ced0c434621228443e7e69f560223ca1.mp4?t=1696030081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Use your Boost to speed run through levels whilst enjoying the adrenaline of going fast!",
  "about_the_game": "Take control of a new prototype spaceship that's been shrunken by new military technology to defeat the Rogue AI which threatens billions of lives with a potential black hole event.<br><br>However, upon infiltration your spaceship has been partially hacked, preventing you from slowing down! Skilfully avoid obstacles controlled by the Rogue AI and ultimately destroy the \"Mega-Brain\".<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109600/extras/9c35817f552e0808b9d91bf52fa8fa4c.poster.avif?t=1696030081\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109600/extras/9c35817f552e0808b9d91bf52fa8fa4c.webm?t=1696030081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109600/extras/9c35817f552e0808b9d91bf52fa8fa4c.mp4?t=1696030081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Master the use of your Boost, Shield, Missiles and Guns to beat the Campaign and unlock Special Operations! Or test your skills in the Infinite Levels that range from Easy to Hard to achieve a High Score on each one.<br><br>All game modes will reward you with Ship Parts which are used to purchase new and better spaceships!<br><br>Fight against the Rogue AI Cyborgs who try to stop you!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109600/extras/e308a9a9cf1be38d7740bcc163050491.poster.avif?t=1696030081\" width=600 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109600/extras/e308a9a9cf1be38d7740bcc163050491.webm?t=1696030081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109600/extras/e308a9a9cf1be38d7740bcc163050491.mp4?t=1696030081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Use your Shield system to become temporarily immune to all damage, as one hit or crash would normally kill you.<br><br>Shoot your missile to deal heavy AoE damage, push certain objects or destroy asteroids and mines.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109600/extras/ced0c434621228443e7e69f560223ca1.poster.avif?t=1696030081\" width=600 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109600/extras/ced0c434621228443e7e69f560223ca1.webm?t=1696030081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2109600/extras/ced0c434621228443e7e69f560223ca1.mp4?t=1696030081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Use your Boost to speed run through levels whilst enjoying the adrenaline of going fast!",
